лонка stage). Тоже самое верно и для обратной ситуации, если у пациента нет рака, то точный диагноз указан в колонке benign_sample_diagnosis. Пропуски в столбце REG1A обусловлены дизайном исследования"],"metadata":{"id":"5r0ES29U0Rb9"},"id":"5r0ES29U0Rb9"},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":4,"id":"3a074798-a35a-4d82-a93d-a6d522a3bcef","metadata":{"id":"3a074798-a35a-4d82-a93d-a6d522a3bcef","outputId":"63a50830-0114-47a4-b20f-da8ecaa7ae7f","colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/","height":175},"executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1773606311896,"user_tz":-180,"elapsed":6,"user":{"displayName":"Daria Lukyanenko","userId":"17896998785669715202"}}},"outputs":[{"output_type":"execute_result","data":{"text/plain":["       sample_id patient_cohort sample_origin  sex stage  \\\n","count        590            590           590  590   199   \n","unique       590              2             4    2     8   \n","top         S590        Cohort1          BPTB    F   III   \n","freq           1            332           409  299    76   \n","\n","       benign_sample_diagnosis  \n","count                      208  \n","unique                      52  \n","top               Pancreatitis  \n","freq                        41  "],"text/html":["\n","  <div id=\"df-a25c5b2d-7047-4a01-a0cc-606baf320923\" class=\"colab-df-container\">\n","    <div>\n","<style scoped>\n","    .dataframe tbody tr th:only-of-type {\n","        vertical-align: middle;\n","    }\n","\n","    .dataframe tbody tr th {\n","        vertical-align: top;\n","    }\n","\n","    .dataframe thead th {\n","        text-align: right;\n","    }\n","</style>\n","<table border=\"1\" class=\"dataframe\">\n","  <thead>\n","    <tr style=\"text-align: right;\">\n","      <th></th>\n","      <th>sample_id</th>\n","      <th>patient_cohort</th>\n","      <th>sample_origin</th>\n","      <th>sex</th>\n","      <th>stage</th>\n","      <th>benign_sample_diagnosis</th>\n","    </tr>\n","  </thead>\n","  <tbody>\n","    <