м на сбалансированность классов:"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":5,"id":"5a7cfe16-c9a9-4e30-a950-2d036f494f32","metadata":{"id":"5a7cfe16-c9a9-4e30-a950-2d036f494f32","outputId":"7f9a3861-26e2-410a-8c95-bc3e22eae840","colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/","height":504},"executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1773606311948,"user_tz":-180,"elapsed":50,"user":{"displayName":"Daria Lukyanenko","userId":"17896998785669715202"}}},"outputs":[{"output_type":"display_data","data":{"text/plain":["<Figure size 800x550 with 1 Axes>"],"image/png":"\n"},"metadata":{}}],"source":["sns.countplot(data=data, x='diagnosis');"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","id":"7d2129ef-8cea-41a8-a17f-c94bde3216bc","metadata":{"id":"7d2129ef-8cea-41a8-a17f-c94bde3216bc"},"source":["Для простоты на данном этапе давайте научимся разделять больных и здоровых пациентов. Если пациент болен - мы будем отправлять его на дообследование и уточнение диагноза. Переобозначим целевой признак (необязательный шаг)"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":6,"id":"5bf7c208-d510-4055-97af-14f7a32c7558","metadata":{"id":"5bf7c208-d510-4055-97af-14f7a32c7558","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1773606311952,"user_tz":-180,"elapsed":2,"user":{"displayName":"Daria Lukyanenko","userId":"17896998785669715202"}}},"outputs":[],"source":["data['diagnosis'] = data['diagnosis'].apply(lambda x: 1 if x >= 2 else 0)"]},{"cell_type":"code","source":["sns.countplot(data=data, x='diagnosis');"],"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/","height":504},"id":"5CZxqH8L1bmT","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1773606312232,"user_tz":-180,"elapsed":277,"user":{"displayName":"Daria Lukyanenko","userId":"17896998785669715202"}},"outputId":"71f73dbf-dc66-4be5-898e-693eaee971c2"},"id":"5CZxqH8L1bmT","execution_count":7,"outputs":[{"output_type":"display_data","data":{"text/plain":["<Figure size 800x550 with 1 Axes>"],"image/png":"\n"},"metadata":{}}]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["1-болен, 0-не болен"],"metadata":{"id":"PuQseIaKCpEl"},"id":"PuQseIaKCpEl"},{"cell_type":"markdown","id":"e7e4059e-79b7-4375-9bac-62a1bfd9a342","metadata":{"id":"e7e4059e-79b7-4375-9bac-62a1bfd9a342"},"source":["Исследуем категориальные признаки"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":8,"id":"97e59404-d247-4313-9198-085354637c71","metadata":{"id":"97e59404-d247-4313-9198-085354637c71","outputId":"e239bb0d-a6a4-41e3-df71-08efb9b4f7dd","colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1773606312243,"user_tz":-180,"elapsed":9,"user":{"displayName":"Daria Lukyanenko","userId":"17896998785669715202"}}},"outputs":[{"output_type":"execute_result","data":{"text/plain":["['sample_id',\n"," 'patient_cohort',\n"," 'sample_origin',\n"," 'sex',\n"," 'stage',\n"," 'benign_sample_diagnosis']"]},"metadata":{},"execution_count":8}],"source":["types = data.dtypes\n","cat_features = list(types[(types == 'object')].index)\n","cat_features"]},{"cell_type":"code","source":["#Уберем колонку sample_id из cat_features, так как это уникальный индекс для каждого пациента\n","cat_features = cat_features[1:]"],"metadata":{"id":"D0L3pPte3gEm","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1773606312246,"user_tz":-180,"elapsed":2,"user":{"displayName":"Daria Lukyanenko","userId":"17896998785669715202"}}},"id":"D0L3pPte3gEm","execution_count":9,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":10,"id":"0c9e03c9-77f8-45ab-9af4-2248926733eb","metadata":{"id":"0c9e03c9-77f8-45ab-9af4-2248926733eb","outputId":"b25fd017-e7ef-45dd-b9b8-d3d41f867dcb","colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/","height":1000},"executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1773606319027,"user_tz":-180,"elapsed":6779,"user":{"displayName":"Daria Lukyanenko","userId":"17896998785669715202"}}},"outputs":[{"output_type":"display_data","data":{"text/plain":["<Figure size 1500x4000 with 10 Axes>"],"image/png":"\n"},"metadata":{}}],"source":["n = len(cat_features) #число категориальных признаков\n","fig, axes = plt.subplots(n, 2, figsize=(15, 40)) #фигура+n*2 координатных плоскостей\n","#Создаем цикл для всех признаков из списка категориальных признаков\n","for i, feature in enumerate(cat_features):\n","    #Строим количественную столбчатую для долевого соотношения каждой из категорий в данных\n","    count_data = (data[feature].value_counts(normalize=True)\n","                  .sort_values(ascending=False)\n","                  .rename('percentage')\n","                  .reset_index())\n","    count_barplot = sns.barplot(data=count_data, x=feature, y='percentage', ax=axes[i][0])\n","    count_barplot.xaxis.set_tick_params(rotation=60)\n","    #Строим столбчатую диаграмму долей по каждому уникальному значению признака в зависимости от категории\n","    mean_barplot = sns.barplot(data=data, x=feature, y='diagnosis', ax=axes[i][1])\n","    mean_barplot.xaxis.set_tick_params(rotation=60)\n","plt.tight_layout() #выравнивание графиков"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","id":"9ecafc9c-aea3-4042-a637-923c4f5f1d88","metadata":{"id":"9ecafc9c-aea3-4042-a637-923c4f5f1d88"},"source":["### Подготовка данных (предобработка)"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","id":"c98823fe-ded7-4116-ab7d-fd10e42dbe30","metadata":{"id":"c98823fe-ded7-4116-ab7d-fd10e42dbe30"},"source":["Предобрабатываем категориальные признаки.\n","\n","Из всего датасета нам понадобится только колонка sex, так как она может потенциально улучшить качество наших предсказаний. Все остальные колонки могут сделать нам target leakage (когда модель будет точно знать диагноз зная только значение одного из этих признаков). Очень важно строить датасет так, как будто мы работаем в реальной клинике, то есть мы провели анализ 4-5 биомаркеров и не знаем никаких других клинических данных."]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":11,"id":"010c58d8-c056-4d58-a975-8f733e44b776","metadata":{"id":"010c58d8-c056-4d58-a975-8f733e44b776","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1773606319034,"user_tz":-180,"elapsed":3,"user":{"displayName":"Daria Lukyanenko","userId":"17896998785669715202"}}},"outputs":[],"source":["copy_data = data.copy()\n","#Бинаризуем переменную \"Пол\"\n","copy_data['sex'] = copy_data['sex'].apply(\n","    lambda x: 1 if x=='F' else 0\n",")"]},{"cell_type":"code","source":["copy_data['sex']"],"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/","height":458},"id":"Qwg0W55s4kXV","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1773606319104,"user_tz":-180,"elapsed":67,"user":{"displayName":"Daria Lukyanenko","userId":"17896998785669715202"}},"outputId":"eedb9b84-6e07-4208-f55b-9a74d4f52fce"},"id":"Qwg0W55s4kXV","execution_count":12,"outputs":[{"output_type":"execute_result","data":{"text/plain":["0      1\n","1      1\n","2      0\n","3      0\n","4      0\n","      ..\n","585    0\n","586    1\n","587    0\n","588    1\n","589    0\n","Name: sex, Length: 590, dtype: int64"],"text/html":["<div>\n","<style scoped>\n","    .dataframe tbody tr th:only-of-type {\n","        vertical-align: middle;\n","    }\n","\n","    .dataframe tbody tr th {\n","        vertical-align: top;\n","    }\n","\n","    .dataframe thead th {\n","        text-align: right;\n","    }\n","</style>\n","<table border=\"1\" class=\"dataframe\">\n","  <thead>\n","    <tr style=\"text-align: right;\">\n","      <th></th>\n","      <th>sex</th>\n","    </tr>\n","  </thead>\n","  <tbody>\n","    <tr>\n","      <th>0</th>\n","      <td>1</td>\n","    </tr>\n","    <tr>\n","      <th>1</th>\n","      <td>1</td>\n","    </tr>\n","    <tr>\n","      <th>2</th>\n","      <td>0</td>\n","    </tr>\n","    <tr>\n","      <th>3</th>\n","      <td>0</td>\n","    </tr>\n","    <tr>\n","      <th>4</th>\n","      <td>0</td>\n","    </tr>\n","    <tr>\n","      <th>...</th>\n","      <td>...</td>\n","    </tr>\n","    <tr>\n","      <th>585</th>\n","      <td>0</td>\n","    </tr>\n","    <tr>\n","      <th>586</th>\n","      <td>1</td>\n","    </tr>\n","    <tr>\n","      <th>587</th>\n","      <td>0</td>\n","    </tr>\n","    <tr>\n","  